title: 4 Pcs Silicone Cake Mold
body_html:
[DIY Any Shape You Love] With our Silicone Cake Mold, you can DIY any shape you like, such as hearts, circles, squares, diamonds, and more! Unleash your creativity and make cakes like no other.

[Safe and Premium Materials] This silicone cake mold is made of 100% premium silicone and is safe to use repeatedly in the microwave, oven, refrigerator, freezer and dishwasher. It can be easily folded and stored without deformation, so you can save space in your kitchen.

[Easy to Clean] This silicone cake mold is easy to remove for cleaning, just wash with soap and water, and it's dishwasher safe.

[Suitable for Many Desserts] This magic cake mold is suitable for making cakes, pizza breads, mousses, jellies, prepared foods, chocolates, puddings, fruit pies and more. It is also a good choice as a gift.

[Specifications]
Material: High Quality Silicone
Size: 7.4 x 2.1 in
Qty: 4 Pcs / 8 Pcs

title: Baking Silicone Clear Stamp
body_html:
Use this Baking Silicone Clear Stamp to make desserts by yourself to surprise family and friends.

[Easy to Use] Just press them on the dessert, you can get the desired pattern, without spending too much time on making, which is very convenient and saves time.

[High Quality Materials] They are made of food grade silica gel, safe and non-toxic, not easy to be damaged and deformed, and can be used for a long time.

[Easy to Clean] After use, only rinse with water, and they are safe for dishwasher.

[Specifications]
Size: About 4 x 6 in / 10 x 15 cm
Material: Food grade silicone material

title: Breakable Heart Silicone Molds
body_html:
If you love romance and surprises, there's no better idea than a gift hidden in chocolate. Soft molds that are easy for even beginners to use allow you to make chocolate without any difficulty!

[Food Grade Silicone] Silicone chocolate heart molds are made of 100% food-grade high-quality silicone, BPA-free, in line with safety standards, environmentally friendly with strong flexibility, and durability, allowing you to use silicone molds for baking safely reliable.

[Easy to Demold ＆ Clean] The smooth, non-stick surface makes the chocolate demold easily, and keeps the perfect 3D diamond heart shape when demolded. It is dishwasher safe and very easy to clean.

[Best Ideas for Celebrations] Adding more happiness and fun by hiding gifts under breakable hearts, it can make the perfect surprising gifts or hand-made decorations for the parties and festivals like birthday, Valentine’s day, Halloween and Christmas. Also the unique but romantic idea for the celebrations like weddings, anniversaries and proposal.

[Specifications]
Material: Food grade high quality silicone
Size: About 8.6 x 7.8 in / 22 x 20 cm

Tips: Please wash before use

title: Kitchen Multifunctional Silicone Mat
body_html:
[Multi Functional] This Mat is used as a trivet, hot pad, hot mat, protector, pot holder, jar opener, utensil rest, drying mat, or anywhere you need extra grip or extreme heat or cold protection.

[Health and Safe] This soft and flexible Mat is made from 100% food-grade silicone. Cyclic use, low energy consumption, green and environmental; Premium silicone material offers that they won't absorb odor, stain, rust, crack, or chip. Can withstand cold and hot temperatures from -40°F to 446°F (from -40°C to 230°C).

[Easy to Wash and Store] This Mat is dishwasher safe and BPA-Free. The hole for easy hanging and convenient storage when not in use.

[Specifications]
Material: food grade high quality silicone
Size: 11.8 in / 30 cm

Create Unique Tasty Treats!
All your tasty treats will look professionally delicious with these nozzle tips - Just simple squeeze on icing bag to create a perfectly round ring with a hollow center that goes well with any toppings! Specifically designed for meringues, icing pastries and cookies.

Delicate Decorations
Easily create layers of swirls, waves, classic french meringue and rings using these nozzle tips!

Easy to Use
Fill the icing bag with your choice of icing and squeeze it to create crisp, sharp meringue shells, or pipe buttercream onto yummy cupcakes!
Versatile Use
Comes with four size for your selection, they are perfect for adding elegant finishing touches on cupcakes, cakes, macarons, cookies, cream puff and more!
Durable, Rust-Resistant
Made of stainless steel metal material, they are rust-resistant and durable without bending out of shape, ensure durability and long-term use.

title: Mini Bunny Silicone Cake Mold
body_html:
Make cute little bunny-shaped cake bites, truffles, or other filled chocolates with this Mini Bunny Silicone Cake Mold!

[Easy to Demold] Just pour your favorite ingredients into the mold and let cool for about 15-20 minutes until fully formed. This flexible silicone mold has a non-stick surface, and with a gentle push from the bottom, the dessert pops instantly.

[Premium Material] The mold is made of 100% pure, professional quality food-grade silicone. BPA, PVC, and Phthalate free. Durable, reliable and non-stick, not easy to deform and easy to clean.

[High temperature resistance] The silicone mold is temperature safe from -40 to +446 °F (-40 to +230 °C) making it dishwasher, oven, microwave, and freezer safe!

[Wide Application] Great for making mousse cake, chocolate candy, pudding, jelly, soap, and more. Perfect for Easter, weddings, birthdays, parties, and more.

[Specifications]
Material: Food Grade Silicone Material
Weight: ≈157g
Size: 11.8 x 6.7 in / 30 x 17 cm

Tips: Please wash before use.

title: Semi Automatic Whisk
body_html:
Semi Automatic Whisk is a great helper for your baking!

[Easy to Use] Designed by the spring mechanical principle, easy to use, just press vertically to stir quickly, saving time and effort while preventing wrist and arm strain. Not batteries, Energy saving and environmental protection.

[Food Grade Material] The egg whisk is made of food-grade stainless steel, durable and not easy to oxidize. The handle is ergonomically designed and easy to hold, making your baking process easier.

[Wide Application] Semi Automatic Whisk can be used not only for beating eggs, but also for mixing, whipping and frothing coffee, milk. Of course, it is also a good tool for making milkshakes, creams and various sauces.

[Easy to Clean] The stainless steel whisk measures 10 inches and fits most containers. After use, simply wash with soapy water.

title: Silicone Pot Strainer
body_html:
[Perfect Food Strainer] Easily attach the strainer to the pot with two sturdy clips, keeping the food in the pot throughout the filtering process, eliminating the hassle of transferring food between the strainer and the pot.

[Universal Design] The specially designed clips will fit nearly all round pots, pans, and big and small bowls (including lipped bowls).

[Easy to Use] Easily strain and drain any liquid from spaghetti, pasta, ground beef, fish, fruits, vegetables and other foods.

[Durable and Heat-resistant] Silicone Pot Strainer is made of safe, non-toxic silicone, BPA free, and can withstand temperatures up to 230°. And is dishwasher safe.

[Specifications]
Material: High quality non-toxic silicone
Size: 9 x 3 in
Temperature Range: -40° ~ 230°

title: Stainless Steel Butter Spreader
body_html:
Cut butter smoothly with this Stainless Steel Butter Spreader!

[Cut Smoothly] Quick spread butter on your toast! Designed with holes that cut butter smooth and effectively without breaking them into pieces!

[Best Performance] Your bread will no longer be torn into pieces, small slotted holes running down the blade edge designed to curl hard butter on your bread. One larger hole designed to curl larger amounts of butter into a rich source of energy on your toast. With the additional Cheese Cutter for those rainy cheese on toast days!

[High Quality & Durable] We have used the highest quality stainless steel to manufacture butter knives. You can use it confidently as it's free from certain impurities and contaminants. This cold butter knife is long-lasting, durable, and highly corrosion-resistant.

[Safe To Use] Ergonomic design and smooth finish ensured safety from injuring yourself accidentally. This butter spread knife is even safe for children to fill their toast with butter/jams and even chocolate curls.

[Specially Designed] We have designed this lovely kitchen tool to be used as a butter spreader and butter curler knife. Beautiful design, perfect weight balance, and 1-inch blade make it perfect to spread the right amount of butter/jams/creams on your toast.

[Specifications]
Material: Stainless Steel
Weight: 66g
Size: 7.8 in
